PRESENTATION PLAN

Start:

Explain prisoners dilemna - 2 Players, Each turn they get a choice (betray or silence), This determines the final score.

PvP Version (Coded onto the microbit, allows two microbit players to play vs each other.)

PvE Version(Several established strategies implemented onto the micro bit each game it will pick one of these random strats.)

Hint application(Python Application, uses machine learning to determine the strategy of the opponent, uses "anti-strategies" to determine the players next "best" move.)
